From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: OpenJoystickDriver <openjoystickdriver@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 21 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] hidapi: honor global joystick HIDAPI hint before hid access

SDL_JOYSTICK_HIDAPI=0 should disable the HIDAPI joystick backend before
hidapi performs platform initialization. On macOS, the hidapi manager
setup can synchronously instantiate IOHID device services, so callers
that explicitly disabled the HIDAPI joystick backend can still block
inside SDL_hid_init().

Check SDL_HINT_JOYSTICK_HIDAPI before SDL_hid_init() so the global
backend hint fully disables HIDAPI joystick initialization. Also skip
HIDAPI joystick detection while the same global hint is disabled, because
the detect path can otherwise call SDL_hid_device_change_count(), which
also initializes hidapi.
---
 src/joystick/hidapi/SDL_hidapijoystick.c | 10 ++++++++++
 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/joystick/hidapi/SDL_hidapijoystick.c b/src/joystick/hidapi/SDL_hidapijoystick.c
index 7629b1ac5..f46b72aca 100644
--- a/src/joystick/hidapi/SDL_hidapijoystick.c
+++ b/src/joystick/hidapi/SDL_hidapijoystick.c
@@ -566,6 +566,12 @@ static bool HIDAPI_JoystickInit(void)
         return true;
     }

+    // Honor the global HIDAPI joystick hint before SDL_hid_init(), since
+    // macOS HID manager setup can synchronously instantiate device services.
+    if (!SDL_GetHintBoolean(SDL_HINT_JOYSTICK_HIDAPI, SDL_HIDAPI_DEFAULT)) {
+        return false;
+    }
+
     if (SDL_hid_init() < 0) {
         return SDL_SetError("Couldn't initialize hidapi");
     }
@@ -1410,6 +1416,10 @@ SDL_GamepadType HIDAPI_GetGamepadTypeFromGUID(SDL_GUID guid)
 static void HIDAPI_JoystickDetect(void)
 {
     if (HIDAPI_StartUpdatingDevices()) {
+        if (!SDL_GetHintBoolean(SDL_HINT_JOYSTICK_HIDAPI, SDL_HIDAPI_DEFAULT)) {
+            HIDAPI_FinishUpdatingDevices();
+            return;
+        }
         Uint32 count = SDL_hid_device_change_count();
         if (SDL_HIDAPI_change_count != count) {
             SDL_HIDAPI_change_count = count;
--
2.50.1
